name: Space Between Us
description:
This painting has been a love hate relationship for 6 months because I wasn’t satisfied. My father was a brilliant muralist that drove himself to drink, depression & death due to his hyper-critical reflection upon his art. I’ve realized through many failures that as long as you are always a student open to learn this unknown future is ever less daunting.
